Description: Designed to simplify the process of retrieving datasets from the 'Big Data PE' platform using secure token-based authentication. It provides functions for securely storing, retrieving, and managing tokens associated with specific datasets, as well as fetching and processing data. The data-retrieval engine is provided by the generic 'apifetch' package, of which 'BigDataPE' is a pre-configured use case.
